---
const posts = [
  "https://www.instagram.com/p/DZt-CgLiL0B/",
  "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYobfwliLPl/",
  "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYoaII2CM57/",
  "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYoYkFTiNJk/",
  "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYoYFToCL3H/",
];
---

<section id="portfolio" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-slate-950">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="text-emerald-400 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Портфолио</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Реальные работы наших мастеров которые вы можете увидеть в нашем Instagramm</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Примеры реставрации ванн.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      {posts.map((url) => (
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg bg-white">
          <iframe 
            src={`${url}embed`} 
            width="100%" 
            height="480" 
            frameborder="0" 
            scrolling="no" 
            allowtransparency="true">
          </iframe>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-10">
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/snowbuilding/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-emerald-400 hover:underline">
        Смотреть больше в Instagram →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
